{"tid":357040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同新拍拖既女人訓覺時想放屁點算","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T15:22:38.000Z","uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d020e363f0b7005e681c37cedde50aa686a9aed9","tid":357040,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"你地都知，老"},{"pid":"33e980d25f6be561c972c2747b98260cf771f529","tid":357040,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"你地都知，老夫老妻梗係大大聲仲要響被入面放都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n但識左幾個月遠遊時同房訓覺，你實會有想放屁既時候架？但識左冇耐我仲未夠膽太放去做呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就忍撚左幾十次，越忍越密，最後頂唔順扮沖多次涼一次過喪放出黎。<br />\n<br />\n但已經搞到好夜，中間仲好鬼辛苦<br />\n<br />\n你地會點處理？"},{"pid":"d65bd2c96567e690d1c443f2a1a2392ff5c28e4b","tid":357040,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"屌你地，竟然冇呢個煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好辛苦，忍屁中途會意外走d小屁出黎已經覺得好唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n仲要死忍，我點釋放心魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbe764de001789ea33b37da2e9d15ffac1500f9","tid":357040,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"哪有女"},{"pid":"4bf6877c8d260d302dc2138d50f2c7376917dd12","tid":357040,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"發展到咩階段？<br />\n去得一齊遠遊無所謂啦？"},{"pid":"6cfc4a0f2f0afecc378cd44d4eb3d744012c4b2d","tid":357040,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發展到咩階段？<br />\n去得一齊遠遊無所謂啦？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2個幾月，過澳門玩only, 冇搞野但有一齊訓，咁好撚監介麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通訓訓下， 砵~~~（你都知長短你好難預，一放就成個出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我相信有人明我個種感受既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3398bbda2d7323940d8ef8f66efcc899a9626f73","tid":357040,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"男人老狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf88958f07079947698b41275e40dbe0dbbc9e78","tid":357040,"uid":135291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"對撚住條女個鼻一次過放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ceed68d3bf927049d60c0b76ff2c016c051e6d","tid":357040,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對撚住條女個鼻一次過放出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放夢都想咁做，肯定好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但現實點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}